definition: fan/sliding, hinged or detachable flat part of sth/classifier for doors, windows etc
to fan/to slap sb on the face

sentences.english: Power will be provided by a single turbofan engine.
sentences.chinese: 電力將提供一個單一的渦扇發動機。

sentences.english: This paper studies the application of model following sliding mode control (MFSMC) to a turbofan engine.
sentences.chinese: 研究了模型跟蹤滑模控制在渦扇發動機控制中的應用。

sentences.english: The validity of the method is testified by monitoring certain type of turbine-fan engine.
sentences.chinese: 通過對某渦扇發動機進行監控，證明該方法確實有效。
